{"tid":1048295,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"演員顏值極高　27歲鄔靖靖挑戰做「最仙氣紀曉芙」","createTime":"2019-03-05T14:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T15:52:32.000Z","uid":12558,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f21040981da8f83048073af74f9afa21f4f581f7","tid":1048295,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"改編自金庸小說的內地電視劇《倚天屠龍記》日前於騰訊首播，雖然新版被不少網民狠批劇情拖拉兼CG效果奇差，但在一片吐槽之下仍然有很多忠實擁躉，皆因演員顏值確實令人驚艷，不少觀眾願意為看演員顏值而「隻眼開隻眼閉」，而由27歲女演員鄔靖靖更擊敗多個經典「紀曉芙」，被網民封做「最有仙氣紀曉芙」！<br />\n<br />\n鄔靖靖畢業於中國傳媒大學南廣學院表演專業系，過往因清純的樣貌兼具有古典氣質而受到青睞，曾參與過不少古裝劇演出。鄔靖靖在新人時期與黃秋生、葉璇等合作古裝傳奇劇《楊貴妃秘史》，並在劇中飾演梅妃的婢女春兒，之後隨即在2011年與阿嬌鍾欣桐、陳浩民、湯怡等合作古裝懸疑劇《大唐女巡按》，逐漸闖出了一點名氣。除了紀曉芙，鄔靖靖其實還有飾演過金庸筆下的角色，就是2014年陳妍希和陳曉主演的的《神鵰俠侶》中愛上楊過的癡情女子公孫綠萼。<br />\n<br />\n但要講到鄔靖靖廣為人知的代表作，就不得不提她於2012年在歷史劇《西施秘史》首次擔大旗做女主角。她在2010年以19歲之齡參加電視劇《西施秘史》的「選西施 拍秘史」活動脫穎而出，最終被挑選飾演絕世美女西施一角。當年劇集一推出後更憑乾淨毫無雜質的非凡脫俗氣質馬上被封做「最清純西施」，更憑住出色表現獲得2012年亞洲偶像盛典「媒體推薦偶像新面孔獎」和海峽兩岸電視藝術節「兩岸交流優秀演員獎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/221203_8a42c0aa5df016bd009c86dc2c36d547.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F221203_8a42c0aa5df016bd009c86dc2c36d547.png&h=13952f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/221204_5e51ef31c2e4e97ff707b9f86699dd77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F221204_5e51ef31c2e4e97ff707b9f86699dd77.png&h=87e82045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/221204_9b43a1e9bb8f36f306a16610033ffaa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F221204_9b43a1e9bb8f36f306a16610033ffaa0.png&h=a75bff2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/221205_3497674178068d028a8a16182c9a8ae8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F221205_3497674178068d028a8a16182c9a8ae8.png&h=572bc3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/221206_8b48a9e4ec9ccf175518e195a9e3f492.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F221206_8b48a9e4ec9ccf175518e195a9e3f492.png&h=958fe21b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18b440d846f2259a838869c3b0d606d4bd0166ec","tid":1048295,"uid":97027,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.beeper.live/images/image/189/18957209.jpg?t=1547568368\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beeper.live%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F189%2F18957209.jpg%3Ft%3D1547568368&h=779dc049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"779ab0c867610f9643eb6e8ca94985368055bd31","tid":1048295,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"呢d女一年出幾百個啦"},{"pid":"94f3436aafefbaad3944bc42cac759c15fd0acdb","tid":1048295,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"求其喺mk執件都有啦"},{"pid":"20fecca59d025c0e9ab84e995fd56fc25220e48d","tid":1048295,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5de5e9d2a5c48adacbd9dd96038aa96319e21065","tid":1048295,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"482f4780c91a30c2115b181461b931af0ee74143","tid":1048295,"uid":4496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"領導,公司老細,導演,副導,編劇,副編,編導,片場助理..."},{"pid":"c309846968bbb62b98fcd77fabeb9d9b5eb7424c","tid":1048295,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"啲記者為炒作真係咩都講得出<br />\n條女根本就好普通"}]}